	<h1>More Clippings</h1><h2><font color="009900">Stray Bullets</font></h2><h3><i>ACM Computers and Society</i></h3><a href="http://sigcas.acm.org/sigcas/subpage/sub_page.cfm?article=543&page_number_nb=1">ACM SIGCAS: The Governance of Code -- Open Land vs. UCITA Land</a>.&nbsp; An interesting article that contrasts the form of governance that results where UCITA is enacted with the situation when software is distributed using open-source principles.&nbsp; There is a good analysis of the Open Source License as well.<br>
